This must be really hard

04:08.000 --> 04:10.000
for you --

04:10.000 --> 04:11.000
you know, the idea

04:10.000 --> 04:11.000
of raising a son when --

04:12.000 --> 04:13.000
Don't start this crap.

04:13.000 --> 04:16.000
I love him just as much

04:13.000 --> 04:16.000
as you do.

04:26.000 --> 04:29.000
Run! Run, run, run!

