She's just gonna come after us

04:39.000 --> 04:41.000
tomorrow

04:41.000 --> 04:44.000
and the next day

04:41.000 --> 04:44.000
and the day after that.

04:44.000 --> 04:46.000
We gotta destroy her.

04:46.000 --> 04:48.000
Or we're never

04:46.000 --> 04:48.000
gonna be safe.

