Did you encounter anything

05:38.000 --> 05:42.000
on your patrol today?

05:42.000 --> 05:44.000
Nothing of note.

05:44.000 --> 05:45.000
Are you certain?

05:45.000 --> 05:46.000
You were gone

05:45.000 --> 05:46.000
for quite some time.

05:46.000 --> 05:48.000
Was there a need

05:46.000 --> 05:48.000
for me?

05:48.000 --> 05:49.000
The creatures are inactive

05:48.000 --> 05:49.000
during the day --

05:50.000 --> 05:52.000
No, no urgent need.

05:52.000 --> 05:53.000
But your prolonged absences

05:52.000 --> 05:53.000
sometimes cause me

05:54.000 --> 05:55.000
to cycle through

05:54.000 --> 05:55.000
various scenarios --

05:55.000 --> 05:58.000
where I have to hypothesize

05:55.000 --> 05:58.000
the nature of your activities.

05:58.000 --> 06:00.000
Perhaps  I  should

05:58.000 --> 06:00.000
start patrolling

06:00.000 --> 06:03.000
while you remain here

06:00.000 --> 06:03.000
with the children.

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
I fear you're not spending

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
enough time with them --

06:05.000 --> 06:07.000
not properly imprinting.

06:13.000 --> 06:15.000
If you could fly, Father.

06:15.000 --> 06:18.000
But on foot, it'll take you

06:15.000 --> 06:18.000
all day to perform the task.

06:20.000 --> 06:24.000
Yes, that is true.

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
But I will try and spend

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
more time with the children.

06:27.000 --> 06:30.000
And perhaps with me,

06:27.000 --> 06:30.000
as well...

06:30.000 --> 06:32.000
I've fashioned

06:30.000 --> 06:32.000
a new joke.

06:32.000 --> 06:34.000
When is a door

06:32.000 --> 06:34.000
not a door?

06:36.000 --> 06:38.000
When it is a jar.

06:36.000 --> 06:38.000
[ajar]

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
A door is always a door,

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
Father.

06:50.000 --> 06:53.000
If our private conversations

06:50.000 --> 06:53.000
interest you, Hunter,

06:53.000 --> 06:54.000
don't strain your ears.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.000
Come join us next time.

06:56.000 --> 06:58.000
I didn't -- I-I --

06:56.000 --> 06:58.000
I'm s-- I'm sorry.

06:58.000 --> 07:00.000
[ Coughs softly ]

07:02.000 --> 07:05.000
[ Humming ]

07:06.000 --> 07:08.000
That's a nice doll

07:06.000 --> 07:08.000
you got there, Vita.

07:08.000 --> 07:10.000
You make it yourself?

07:10.000 --> 07:12.000
Tally taught me.

07:12.000 --> 07:13.000
Tally?

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
The girl who used to sleep

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
in my bed.

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
You shouldn't talk

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
about her, Vita.

07:21.000 --> 07:24.000
She's dead.

07:24.000 --> 07:26.000
There you are.

07:24.000 --> 07:26.000
It's bedtime.

07:26.000 --> 07:28.000
Father is

07:26.000 --> 07:28.000
looking for you.

07:28.000 --> 07:31.000
[ "Twinkle, Twinkle,

07:28.000 --> 07:31.000
Little Star" playing off-key ]

07:40.000 --> 07:44.000
Are you feeling positive

07:40.000 --> 07:44.000
about your baby today?

07:44.000 --> 07:48.000
No matter how many times

07:44.000 --> 07:48.000
you ask me that question,

07:48.000 --> 07:50.000
the answer's always

07:48.000 --> 07:50.000
gonna be the same.

07:50.000 --> 07:54.000
Then I'll have to ask you

07:50.000 --> 07:54.000
to reaffirm your promise to me.

07:54.000 --> 07:59.000
I promise I'm not gonna try

07:54.000 --> 07:59.000
and kill myself or the baby.

07:59.000 --> 08:01.000
Thank you.

08:03.000 --> 08:04.000
Now put that away.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.000
You need to sleep.

08:05.000 --> 08:07.000
When I figure out

08:05.000 --> 08:07.000
this song.

08:11.000 --> 08:13.000
Nightmares are only thoughts,

08:11.000 --> 08:13.000
Tempest.

08:13.000 --> 08:14.000
They're not real.

08:14.000 --> 08:16.000
Not what I see.

08:16.000 --> 08:18.000
What I see

08:16.000 --> 08:18.000
really happened.

08:18.000 --> 08:20.000
And every time

08:18.000 --> 08:20.000
I close my eyes,

08:20.000 --> 08:22.000
it feels like

08:20.000 --> 08:22.000
it's happening to me again.

08:22.000 --> 08:24.000
But what would you know?

08:24.000 --> 08:26.000
You don't even

08:24.000 --> 08:26.000
have nightmares.

08:29.000 --> 08:31.000
Or do you?

08:33.000 --> 08:35.000
No.

08:37.000 --> 08:40.000
I have complete over

08:37.000 --> 08:40.000
my mind's functioning --

08:40.000 --> 08:42.000
no matter

08:40.000 --> 08:42.000
what mode I'm in.

08:44.000 --> 08:46.000
Do you wish

08:44.000 --> 08:46.000
you could have them?

08:46.000 --> 08:50.000
Not nightmares,

08:46.000 --> 08:50.000
but dreams.

08:52.000 --> 08:55.000
I do not wish for things.

08:55.000 --> 08:58.000
I'm not one who wants.

08:55.000 --> 08:58.000
I'm one who serves.

08:58.000 --> 09:05.000
♪♪

09:05.000 --> 09:07.000
Will you stay with me?

09:10.000 --> 09:12.000
Of course.

