12:26.000 --> 12:29.000
three sticks.

12:29.000 --> 12:32.000
This puzzle's

12:29.000 --> 12:32.000
pretty hard.

12:32.000 --> 12:34.000
How long did it take me again,

12:32.000 --> 12:34.000
Mother?

