It took you 23 minutes and

12:34.000 --> 12:38.000
35 seconds to solve this one,

12:38.000 --> 12:40.000
which is somewhat faster

12:38.000 --> 12:40.000
than the average

12:40.000 --> 12:43.000
for a child your age.

12:43.000 --> 12:47.000
Not all stick puzzles

12:43.000 --> 12:47.000
take that long, but some do.

12:51.000 --> 12:53.000
Do you need a hint?

12:53.000 --> 12:56.000
Let Paul try and figure it out

12:53.000 --> 12:56.000
on his own.

12:56.000 --> 12:57.000
The lesson doesn't work

12:58.000 --> 13:00.000
if the answer is given

12:58.000 --> 13:00.000
prior to the work.

13:02.000 --> 13:03.000
No, I think I got it.

13:11.000 --> 13:14.000
Very impressive,

13:11.000 --> 13:14.000
Paul.

13:14.000 --> 13:16.000
You cheated.

13:14.000 --> 13:16.000
Campion --

13:16.000 --> 13:18.000
No, I didn't. I didn't.

13:16.000 --> 13:18.000
You already knew this one.

13:18.000 --> 13:19.000
No, I swear, I just...

13:18.000 --> 13:19.000
figured it out.

13:19.000 --> 13:21.000
This is not

13:19.000 --> 13:21.000
a competition.

13:21.000 --> 13:24.000
It's a lesson in --

13:21.000 --> 13:24.000
in solving problems.

13:32.000 --> 13:34.000
Campion?

13:35.000 --> 13:38.000
[ Wind whistling ]

14:00.000 --> 14:02.000
What are you doing?

14:03.000 --> 14:05.000
What was that?

14:03.000 --> 14:05.000
Shh. It's nothing.

14:03.000 --> 14:05.000
Go back to bed.

14:06.000 --> 14:09.000
We're not on the ark anymore.

14:06.000 --> 14:09.000
You can't tell me what to do.

14:11.000 --> 14:13.000
Fine.

14:11.000 --> 14:13.000
Should I call Mother?

14:14.000 --> 14:15.000
Maybe you can show her

14:14.000 --> 14:15.000
what you're hiding.

14:15.000 --> 14:18.000
Wait, wait, wait.

14:15.000 --> 14:18.000
Holly, Holly, Holly, Holly.

14:23.000 --> 14:25.000
[ Sniffs ]

14:25.000 --> 14:27.000
It's still fresh.

14:27.000 --> 14:28.000
Where did you find this?

14:28.000 --> 14:31.000
I found it when we were

14:28.000 --> 14:31.000
searching for firewood.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.000
There must be survivors.

14:33.000 --> 14:35.000
Probably gonna rescue us.

14:35.000 --> 14:37.000
What about

14:35.000 --> 14:37.000
Father and Mother?

14:37.000 --> 14:39.000
I like them.

14:37.000 --> 14:39.000
I don't want them to be hurt.

14:39.000 --> 14:41.000
I know, but it's only

14:39.000 --> 14:41.000
a matter of time

14:41.000 --> 14:42.000
before she decides

14:41.000 --> 14:42.000
it's too much trouble

14:42.000 --> 14:44.000
to keep those eyes out,

14:42.000 --> 14:44.000
and then -- poof!

14:44.000 --> 14:46.000
There'll be

14:44.000 --> 14:46.000
five more gravestones

14:46.000 --> 14:47.000
with our names on them.

14:47.000 --> 14:50.000
[ Scoffs ]

14:47.000 --> 14:50.000
That's not gonna happen.

14:52.000 --> 14:54.000
Famous last words.

14:54.000 --> 15:02.000
♪♪

15:02.000 --> 15:09.000
♪♪

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
Your Eminence,

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
in case I should die

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
during the course of our action

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
to reclaim the children,

15:14.000 --> 15:16.000
I'd like to --

15:14.000 --> 15:16.000
I'd like to take this moment

15:16.000 --> 15:19.000
to express my deepest gratitude

15:16.000 --> 15:19.000
for your decision

15:19.000 --> 15:23.000
to forgive my father

15:19.000 --> 15:23.000
his mortal sin.

15:23.000 --> 15:25.000
You know the whole story?

15:25.000 --> 15:28.000
Oh, I mean, I know what's

15:25.000 --> 15:28.000
in the official report.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.000
Now that you mention it,

15:28.000 --> 15:29.000
it was a bit scant.

15:29.000 --> 15:33.000
Okay, why don't you tell me

15:29.000 --> 15:33.000
what was in the report?

15:33.000 --> 15:34.000
Maybe there's something

15:33.000 --> 15:34.000
I can add.

15:35.000 --> 15:36.000
The report said

15:35.000 --> 15:36.000
your platoon picked up

15:36.000 --> 15:40.000
an atheist child soldier,

15:36.000 --> 15:40.000
a female.

